d Instagram Ads allow you to create specific, customized audiences and get your best ads in front of your ideal customers.<\/p>\n<div data-embed-button=\"images\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:media.simple_image\" data-entity-type=\"media\" data-entity-uuid=\"eddc7160-730b-4e17-9615-840a1211004a\" data-langcode=\"und\" class=\"embedded-entity align-center\">\n<article>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/ppc-training-facebook-ad-example-1.png\" width=\"401\" height=\"478\" alt=\"ppc-training-mvmt-facebook-ad-example\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" \/><\/div>\n<\/article>\n<\/div>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">When done correctly, PPC can help a small business catalyze an immense amount of growth. Likewise, adding PPC as a service offering can help a digital marketing agency bring in tons more revenue year over year.<\/p>\n<p>There\u2019s only one problem: <strong>When you\u2019re on your own, PPC is difficult and time-consuming<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>Everything we do at WordStream is motivated by our goal to help small businesses and digital marketing agencies succeed with PPC. That\u2019s why we\u2019ve assembled a master list of all the PPC training resources you need to start succeeding with online advertising. Let\u2019s dive in!<\/p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Guided PPC training courses<\/h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In the following sections, we\u2019ll connect you to a ton of individual PPC training resources (blog posts, articles, etc.) that you can browse at your own pace. If, however, you\u2019d like a more guided PPC training experience, we recommend checking out PPC University and Growth Academy.<\/p>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">PPC University<\/h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ready to hit the books? If you\u2019re looking for a free, carefully structured learning experience, WordStream\u2019s <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/learn\">PPC University<\/a> is the resource for you. With in-depth yet digestible lessons divided across four courses\u2014PPC 101, PPC 102, Advanced PPC, and Social Ads 101\u2014PPC University offers the accessible, comprehensive PPC training you\u2019ve been searching for.<\/p>\n<p>Best of all: You can take your PPC training on the go! Equipped with a library of free, downloadable whitepapers, PPC University is perfect for aspiring digital marketers with jam-packed schedules.<\/p>\n<p><span><div class='et-box et-shadow'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class='et-box-content'>\u2734\ufe0f <strong>Free download<\/strong> &gt;&gt; <\/span><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/marketing.wordstream.com\/WSLIQContentDLPPC101.html?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_PPC_PPC101_Download\" class=\"waffle-rich-text-link\">PPC 101: The Beginner&#8217;s Guide to PPC<\/a><\/strong><span><\/div><\/div><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">PPC training resources: Search engine marketing<\/h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Search engine marketing (SEM) is the branch of PPC that focuses on turning <strong>active user intent<\/strong> into valuable website traffic. As you\u2019ll see throughout the PPC training experience, PPC and SEM are often used interchangeably. Terminology aside, the basic goal is to earn top sponsored search results on Google and Bing and entice your prospects with relevant, intent-matching offers. Check out these resources to learn everything you need to know to get started with SEM:<\/p>\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/search-engine-marketing\">SEM: What It Is &amp; How to Do It Right<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/keyword\">What Are Keywords &amp; Why Do They Matter for PPC?<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/keyword-match-types\">What Are Keyword Match Types &amp; How Should You Use Them?<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2018\/06\/06\/negative-keyword-guide\">The Definitive Guide to Negative Keywords<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/ad-groups\">How to Create More Effective Ad Groups for PPC<\/a